# Notes (local / generated)
# - HumanNote: 人类权威笔记（通常含隐私/大量变更，不建议入库）
# - RobotNote: Agent 生成输出（每次 run 可能被覆盖）
HumanNote/*
!HumanNote/README.md
!HumanNote/Steps/
HumanNote/Steps/*
!HumanNote/Steps/steps_guide.md

RobotNote/*
!RobotNote/README.md
